cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.NI, cs.SE, cs.SI 

The paper discusses security assessment of IoT networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of SIEM logs and dynamic activity metrics suggests the involvement of information retrieval (cs.IR) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The proposal of attack circuits and attack graphs indicates the use of graph theory and algorithms (cs.SE) and system and information theory (cs.SI).
